# Next.js web (`apps/web`)

- App Router under `src/app/`. Use `@/` imports (`@/components`, `@/lib`).
- shadcn UI in `src/components/ui/`; merge classes with `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`.
- Call API via `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` (see `health-panel.tsx`). No hardcoded production URLs.
- Client components: `'use client'` when using hooks or browser APIs.
- Unit tests go in `apps/web/specs/`, not under `src/`. Production build needs `NODE_ENV=production`.
- Enable `output: 'standalone'` in `next.config.js` when changing Docker deploy paths.
